5D201C8E.Line1.B20BA: It’s a past I hold no pride for. Stained with death - and not all deserving.

91090F92.Line5.B20BA: I put the “Bear” to rest long ago…

F7149610.Line3.B20BA: My hands were not my own. They were tools of Stana, wielded against any who drew her ire. Sometimes… for amusement alone.
